Package it.polimi.ingsw.utils.jsonCreator

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    DevelopmentCard2JSON
    Class used to convert the input given into a JSON representation of a DevelopmentCard In order to easily correct the input error, there will be create 48 JSON file one for each DevelopmentCard To have an unique JSON it must be used DevelopmentCard2JSON
    DevelopmentCardJoinJSON
    Class used to merge together many JSON representing DevelopmentCard
    LeaderCard2JSON
    Class used to convert the input given into a JSON representation of a LeaderCard In order to easily correct the input error, there will be create 16 JSON file one for each LeaderCard To have an unique JSON it must be used LeaderCardJoinJSON
    LeaderCardJoinJSON
    Class used to merge together many JSON representing LeaderCard It's suggested to merge together LeaderCard with the same power
